								</svg>
							</div>
							<h3 class="offer-card-title">Water Heater</h3>
							<p class="offer-card-value">FREE</p>
							<p class="offer-card-desc">Standard water heater installation - reliable hot water for your home</p>
						</div>
						<div class="offer-card">
							<div class="offer-card-icon">
								<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
								</svg>
							</div>
							<h3 class="offer-card-title">Or Save Cash</h3>
							<p class="offer-card-value">$1,500 OFF</p>
							<p class="offer-card-desc">Take $1,500 off your new Trane HVAC system installation</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Contact Form Section -->
			<section class="form-section" id="contact-form">
				<div class="container">
					<div class="form-container">
						<div class="form-info">
							<h2 class="form-info-title">
								Claim Your <span class="highlight">Free Offer</span>
							</h2>
							<p class="form-info-text">
								Fill out the form and our team will contact you to schedule your free consultation. No obligation, no pressure - just honest HVAC advice from local experts.
							</p>
							<ul class="form-benefits">
								<li>
									<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
										<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
									</svg>
									<span>Free in-home consultation</span>
								</li>
								<li>
									<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
										<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
									</svg>
									<span>No-obligation quote</span>
								</li>
								<li>
									<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
										<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
									</svg>
									<span>Financing options available</span>
								</li>
								<li>
									<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
										<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
									</svg>
									<span>Licensed & insured professionals</span>
								</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
						<div class="form-wrapper">
							<form
								class="winter-form"
								name={formName}
								method="POST"
								data-netlify="true"
								data-netlify-honeypot="bot-field"
								action="/submit-quote"
							>
								<!-- Netlify hidden fields -->
								<input type="hidden" name="form-name" value={formName} />
								<input type="hidden" name="offer" value="Winter Special 2026" />
								<p class="hidden">
									<label>
										Don't fill this out if you're human: <input name="bot-field" />
									</label>
								</p>

								<h3 class="form-title">Get Your Free Quote</h3>

								<div class="form-row">
									<div class="form-group">
										<label for="name" class="form-label">Name *</label>
										<input type="text" id="name" name="name" class="form-input" required placeholder="Your full name" />
									</div>
									<div class="form-group">
										<label for="phone" class="form-label">Phone *</label>
										<input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" class="form-input" required placeholder="(555) 555-5555" />
									</div>
								</div>

								<div class="form-row">
									<div class="form-group">
										<label for="email" class="form-label">Email *</label>
										<input type="email" id="email" name="email" class="form-input" required placeholder="your@email.com" />
									</div>
									<div class="form-group">
										<label for="zip" class="form-label">Zip Code *</label>
										<input type="text" id="zip" name="zip" class="form-input" required placeholder="85001" pattern="[0-9]{5}" maxlength="5" />
									</div>
								</div>

								<div class="form-group full-width">
									<label class="form-label">Are you a homeowner? *</label>
									<div class="radio-group">
										<label class="radio-option">
											<input type="radio" name="homeowner" value="yes" required />
											<span>Yes</span>
										</label>
										<label class="radio-option">
											<input type="radio" name="homeowner" value="no" />
											<span>No</span>
										</label>
									</div>
								</div>

								<div class="form-group full-width">
									<label class="checkbox-group">
										<input type="checkbox" name="terms" value="agreed" required />
										<span class="checkbox-label">
											I agree to the terms and conditions. I understand this offer ends March 31st, 2026 and is subject to the requirements listed below. Arizona homeowners only.
										</span>
									</label>
								</div>

								<button type="submit" class="form-submit">Claim My Free Offer</button>
							</form>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Terms Section -->
			<section class="terms-section">
				<div class="container">
					<div class="terms-box">
						<h3 class="terms-title">Terms & Conditions</h3>
						<ul class="terms-list">
							<li><strong>Offer Deadline:</strong> Special ends on March 31st, 2026</li>
							<li><strong>Minimum Purchase:</strong> Trane HVAC system purchase of $12,000.00 or more required</li>
							<li><strong>Mini-Split Specifications:</strong> Mini-split size is up to 24000 BTU</li>
							<li><strong>Electrical Requirements:</strong> There must be room in the electrical panel for the required circuit</li>
							<li><strong>Installation Limits:</strong> Electrical run to mini-split must be less than 30'</li>
							<li><strong>Additional Fees:</strong> Any work needed outside of these parameters will not be included in the deal and will require additional fees</li>
							<li><strong>Water Heater:</strong> Standard water heater installation only, no tankless</li>
							<li><strong>Eligibility:</strong> Arizona homeowners only</li>
						</ul>
						<span class="terms-deadline">Offer expires March 31st, 2026</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
		<FooterMain />

		<!-- Mobile Sticky CTA -->
		<div class="mobile-sticky-cta">
			<a href="#contact-form">Claim Your Free Offer</a>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
